Product description

NeoStreak men's Light Blue slim fit stretch jeans brings the latest trend for the fashion conscious. High on style and quality, these Light Blue solid pattern jeans are as versatile as they are comfortable - a must have in your wardrobe. Ideal for casual and party wear, Pair these uber cool jeans with any light color NeoStreak shirt or t-shirt, and never go out of style!.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
